title.rendered: Canon T7 EOS Rebel DSLR Camera with EF-S 18-55mm f/3.5-5.6 is II Lens and Wide-Angle Lens Attachment + Battery Power Kit + 64GB SD Card Platinum…

content.rendered:
• Bright optical viewfinder and large 3.0″ 920k-dot LCD monitor for live view shooting and image playback. Scene Intelligent Auto Mode
  • Advanced 9-point AF with center cross-type point, ISO 100-6400 can be extended to 12800, and 3fps continuous shooting
  • Built-in Wi-Fi and NFC technology for easy online sharing, EF-S 18-55mm f/3.5-5.6 IS II Lens included
  • Photo Savings platinum bundle packed with value photo accessories including Premium DSLR Backpack, Flash w/ Diffusers, Camera Straps, Cleaning Equipment, and much more (See Description)
